#: views/public/index/index.php:18
msgid "Verifying your browser"
msgstr "Vérification du navigateur"

#: views/public/index/index.php:93
msgid "JavaScript required"
msgstr "JavaScript requis"

#: views/public/index/index.php:94
msgid "Please enable JavaScript in your browser to access this site."
msgstr ""
"Veuillez activer JavaScript dans votre navigateur pour accéder à ce site."

#: views/public/index/index.php:99
msgid "Verifying your browser…"
msgstr "Vérification du navigateur…"

#: views/public/index/index.php:101
msgid "This is an automatic process. Please wait."
msgstr "Il s'agit d'un processus automatique. Veuillez patienter."

#: views/public/index/index.php:105
#, php-format
msgid "Powered by %s"
msgstr "Propulsé par %s"

#: views/public/index/index.php:137
msgid "Automated browser detected. Access denied."
msgstr "Navigateur automatisé détecté. Accès refusé."

#: views/public/index/index.php:157
msgid "Verified. Redirecting…"
msgstr "Vérifié. Redirection…"

#: views/admin/plugins/bot-challenge-config-form.php:8
msgid "HMAC salt"
msgstr "Sel HMAC"

#: views/admin/plugins/bot-challenge-config-form.php:12
msgid ""
"Secret salt used to generate challenge tokens. Leave empty to regenerate "
"automatically. Changing this value invalidates all existing cookies."
msgstr ""
"Sel secret utilisé pour créer des jetons de défi. Laisser vide pour le "
"régénérer automatiquement. La modification de cette valeur invalide tous les "
"cookies existants."

#: views/admin/plugins/bot-challenge-config-form.php:19
msgid "Challenge delay (seconds)"
msgstr "Délai du défi (secondes)"

#: views/admin/plugins/bot-challenge-config-form.php:23
msgid "Number of seconds the visitor must wait before the cookie is set."
msgstr ""
"Nombre de secondes à attendre pour le visiteur vant de placer le cookie."

#: views/admin/plugins/bot-challenge-config-form.php:30
msgid "Cookie lifetime (days)"
msgstr "Durée de vie des cookies (jours)"

#: views/admin/plugins/bot-challenge-config-form.php:34
msgid "Number of days the challenge cookie remains valid."
msgstr "Nombre de jours pendant lesquels le cookie reste valide."

#: views/admin/plugins/bot-challenge-config-form.php:41
msgid "Detect headless browsers"
msgstr "Détecter les navigateurs sans tête"

#: views/admin/plugins/bot-challenge-config-form.php:45
msgid ""
"Run additional tests to detect headless browsers (Selenium, PhantomJS, "
"Puppeteer, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Exécuter des tests supplémentaires pour détecter les navigateurs sans tête "
"(Selenium, PhantomJS, Puppeteer, etc.)."

#: views/admin/plugins/bot-challenge-config-form.php:52
msgid "Exception paths"
msgstr "Exceptions pour les chemins"

#: views/admin/plugins/bot-challenge-config-form.php:56
msgid ""
"Url path prefixes to exclude from the challenge, one per line. Example: /api"
msgstr ""
"Préfixes de chemins d'url à exclure du défi, un par ligne. Exemple : /api"

#: views/admin/plugins/bot-challenge-config-form.php:63
msgid "Exception IPs"
msgstr "Exceptions pour les ips"

#: views/admin/plugins/bot-challenge-config-form.php:67
msgid ""
"Ips v4 or v6 or cidr ranges to exclude from the challenge, one per line."
msgstr "Plages ips v4 ou v6 ou cidr à exclure du défi, une par ligne."
